<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="past-adj">past <strong><em>adj</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /pɑːst/    美 /pæst/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>过去的；以往的；结束了的：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Great changes have taken place in the school over / in the past three years.
在过去三年里，这所学校发生了巨大的变化。</p><footer>2011 福建书面表达改</footer></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The club is holding a party for past and present members. 
俱乐部正在为前会员和现会员举办聚会。</p><footer>2012 上海</footer></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Winter is past and spring has come. 
冬去春来。</p></div>

